<body>
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="terminal">
        <h1><span class="errorcode"><%= info[pid - 1].TITLE %></span> - <%= info[pid - 1].SCORE %></h1>

        <p>You can enter the commands listed below.</p>
        <p class="output">solve --answer=[answer key]</p>
        <p class="output">solve -a=[answer key]</p>

        <br>
        <p>Enter <a href="/challenge">challenges</a> to return the challenges page.</p>

